                <li><strong>Seamless State Syncing</strong> achieved between smartwatch and smartphone, maintaining sub-second accuracy across real-time Wear OS health metrics.</li>
                <li><strong>Resilient Architecture</strong> ensured continuous GPS map trajectory recording even during deep cellular network drops or Doze mode cycles.</li>
                <li><strong>Rapid Deployment Pipeline</strong> enabled through strict Dynamic Feature Modularization and Custom Gradle Convention Plugins.</li>
            </ul>
